     <td>This tutorial is a step in the <a href="../../forms/using/create-your-first-adaptive-form.md">Create Your First Adaptive Form</a> series. It is recommended to follow the series in chronological sequence to understand, perform, and demonstrate the complete tutorial use case.</td> 
